{"tid":1533781,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎睇下自已係和理非定左膠","createTime":"2019-09-02T22:00:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T14:52:57.000Z","uid":63822,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"50c43048fd2dd6b5d9d9226ee9b4fae2ba700f8d","tid":1533781,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T22:00:23.000Z","msg":"和理非：保護手足，抵擋政權<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/487izS4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F487izS4.gif&h=3377822e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠：保護政權，阻擋手足<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7s8mxFq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7s8mxFq.gif&h=54c07e84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非唔係要防止手足做錯事，而係手足做錯事之後，盡全力補鑊<br />\n<br />\n手足未做野你就先入為主要阻人行動既，就為之左膠<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n勇武一日唔轉守為攻，一日都停止唔到送頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1517066\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1517066</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我媽媽經歷過文化大革命，有少少野想同大家講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1456583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1456583</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n跳閘+罷買站內商舖，狗鐵每日損失7000萬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1506335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1506335</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e392a1833f8e57e34f9faf33d4c7730f67500d01","tid":1533781,"uid":289649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T22:00:56.000Z","msg":"明白大家呢排嘅士氣經過<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">831恐襲</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">901大撤退</span></span>之後好低落<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我同大家一樣都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但越係呢啲時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">我地就越要堅持下去，<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">團結一致</span></span><br />\n唔好比林鄭見我地冇士氣而去捉多啲人<br />\n<br />\n以下兩篇文章<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無論<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理非</span>，定係<span style=\"color: red;\">勇武</span>，都應該入黎，打返枝<span style=\"color: violet;\">強心針</span></span><br />\n<br />\n希望可以幫到大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得share比身邊因近日事件而唔開心嘅朋友仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［全部人同我入黎］《致眾表》望各位香港市民出自己的一份綿力<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1532967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1532967</a><br />\n<br />\n灰心喪志，是因為你看不見抗爭的前路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533741\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533741</a>"},{"pid":"f4f5a01c5ea9f5f3183704352231f0a75b01f3d4","tid":1533781,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:32:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"92c9d36c85642098def7b013dc8335fb1e45db66","tid":1533781,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:33:52.000Z","msg":"仲有個之前頂住防暴隊個盾"},{"pid":"9aa6fe1884857b1c07511b6b4d7737d3ffa6d2e7","tid":1533781,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:36:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://gfycat.com/sarcasticidealkatydid\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgfycat.com%2Fsarcasticidealkatydid&h=65189060&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b0ac1a22fe884c73856107c6229f5149690de68","tid":1533781,"uid":140326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:36:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gfycat.com/sarcasticidealkatydid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgfycat.com%2Fsarcasticidealkatydid&d=7ie9SmB3qTQYrTFhvLfIgUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=3f8f5cd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gfycat.com/sarcasticidealkatydid</a>"},{"pid":"1c43d80b52a06e62e3508a920388db5575b57b70","tid":1533781,"uid":315924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:36:46.000Z","msg":"［重開］江蛇對仔女:er&hellip;點解學校冇人同我玩？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1533827\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1533827</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de9178d91ad9670be8581392e70e8a442a6a2d2d","tid":1533781,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:37:26.000Z","msg":"好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠同中立撚真係最仆街"},{"pid":"483ae5fce8d3f7ad39aed542d4240a2e748847a1","tid":1533781,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:49:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，十月一前每日堅持做以下嘅動作。係堅持，堅唔到都要堅持，請發誓你可以堅持成個九月：<br />\n<br />\n1. 永遠抵制任何福建幫以及元朗鄉黑嘅商鋪、藍紅食店、cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸。仲有記得逢星期五同日都罷買！好重要！記得搭黨鐵都要跳閘！好重要！<br />\n<br />\n2. 低娛樂（閒時要做運動發洩、晚晚十點窗邊鳩叫、拒絕淘寶！）<br />\n3. 每日簽最少1個聯署（實搵到）<br />\n4. 全民打多條國際文宣戰線 (Twitter, Reddit)<br />\n5. 每星期最少參與1次行動，無行動去商場涼冷氣，理性咁教育自由行。<br />\n6. 每星期去連儂貼3張文宣<br />\n7. 出糧提款換美金<br />\n8. 唔好買入任何大陸公司股票<br />\n9. 轉埋你個MPF去外地基金<br />\n10. 不要說推，試著將呢整個訊息copy and paste嚟推post#kill<br />\n11. Tag或催你身邊三個人一齊參與<br />\n歡迎幫手整合同加事件。加油，相信我哋日日都做到。只有200萬人堅持經濟抗爭先可以制裁佢地。<br />\n<br />\n利申：我做緊。Best effort 。你呢？"},{"pid":"11343eb1b5b062c3db6a6c69c789d2606a5ea13b","tid":1533781,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de9178d91ad9670be8581392e70e8a442a6a2d2d","tid":1533781,"uid":261914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T23:37:26.000Z","msg":"好例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n左膠同中立撚真係最仆街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T07:55:32.000Z","msg":"轉搞自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a545911d518c8db98f9b4d8ca9054cbfdfeba5","tid":1533781,"uid":234352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"